query:
SELECT 
  name,
  checkInDate,
  checkOutDate,
  FROM_UNIXTIME(checkInDate/1000) as checkInUTC,
  FROM_UNIXTIME(checkOutDate/1000) as checkOutUTC
FROM hotels
WHERE tripId = 30001 AND name LIKE '%Vivendi%';
